ver agreement for all other scores was moderate to almost perfect (AC(2)  = 0.61-0.82). Intraobserver agreement was substantial to almost perfect for all parameters (AC(2)  = 0.76-1.0). DATA CONCLUSION: Prospective RT with bellows can effectively minimize ghosting artifact and improve image quality for brachial plexus MRI within clinically optimal acquisition times. LEVEL OF EVIDENCE: 1 Technical Efficacy: Stage 2.
