y valuable technique for objectively estimating the severity of PHN pain, which would provide an opportunity for elucidating the central mechanisms underlying PHN as well. KEY WORDS: Postherpetic neuralgia, diffusional kurtosis imaging, insula cortex, gray matter, voxel-based analysis.
